    dc:description "FIGURE29.Lateral habitus photographs of tetrigid grasshopper hosts (antennae broken inboth specimens).(A) Loxilobus sp., type host specimen for Podotarsonemus australiensis sp. nov. (B) Hedotettix amplus (Sjöstedt), type host specimen for Podotarsonemus queenslandensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1242493/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

